  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>Roadmap</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/3ded6198728e7b85cb568f60fe83a3ba.avif?t=1714559109\" width=600 height=326 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Adarin Farm is a roguelite farm simulation game. Plant & harvest fruits to fulfill requests, improve your farm with rare fertilizers & combine dozens of blessings to maximize your profits! <br><br>Plant and loot your way to victory!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Plant & Harvest</h2>Plant seeds and harvest fruits from fantasy crops. Each seed has a randomized effect that will have an impact on your run.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/e55b21be3af13b79cc91e6964b6b5531.poster.avif?t=1714559109\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/e55b21be3af13b79cc91e6964b6b5531.webm?t=1714559109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/e55b21be3af13b79cc91e6964b6b5531.mp4?t=1714559109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Loot to improve your farm</h2>While harvesting or completing requests, you have access to a large variety of randomized rarity fertilizers that you will use on your fields. These fertilizers will give you major bonuses.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/67dc0243d60a80241f92b6b17e6736a1.poster.avif?t=1714559109\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/67dc0243d60a80241f92b6b17e6736a1.webm?t=1714559109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/67dc0243d60a80241f92b6b17e6736a1.mp4?t=1714559109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combine Blessings</h2>Choose between dozen of randomly generated Blessings to tailor your run. Combine them for maximum efficiency!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/418252a33a950272aa8b660970beb204.poster.avif?t=1714559109\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/418252a33a950272aa8b660970beb204.webm?t=1714559109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/418252a33a950272aa8b660970beb204.mp4?t=1714559109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Complete requests</h2>Sell your fruits to earn gold and runes!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/5b9b2b10225341b770cdddc424c29550.poster.avif?t=1714559109\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/5b9b2b10225341b770cdddc424c29550.webm?t=1714559109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/5b9b2b10225341b770cdddc424c29550.mp4?t=1714559109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "Adarin Farm is a roguelite farm simulation game. Plant & harvest fruits to fulfill requests, improve your farm with rare fertilizers & combine dozens of blessings to maximize your profits! <br><br>Plant and loot your way to victory!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Plant & Harvest</h2>Plant seeds and harvest fruits from fantasy crops. Each seed has a randomized effect that will have an impact on your run.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/e55b21be3af13b79cc91e6964b6b5531.poster.avif?t=1714559109\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/e55b21be3af13b79cc91e6964b6b5531.webm?t=1714559109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/e55b21be3af13b79cc91e6964b6b5531.mp4?t=1714559109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Loot to improve your farm</h2>While harvesting or completing requests, you have access to a large variety of randomized rarity fertilizers that you will use on your fields. These fertilizers will give you major bonuses.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/67dc0243d60a80241f92b6b17e6736a1.poster.avif?t=1714559109\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/67dc0243d60a80241f92b6b17e6736a1.webm?t=1714559109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1827730/extras/67dc0243d60a80241f92b6b17e6736a1.mp4?t=1714559109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combine Blessings</h2>Choose